{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"729c070b-6134-40d2-b8e3-7bc3313ab0a6","content":"Here's what to change:\n\n### `.csproj` changes\n\n1. **Remove** the old assembly reference to `Microsoft.VisualStudio.QualityTools.UnitTestFramework`\n2. **Add** the unified `MSTest` v3 NuGet package (replaces the old `MSTest.TestFramework` + `MSTest.TestAdapter` split)\n3. **Update** `Microsoft.NET.Test.Sdk` to a current version\n\n```xml\n<!-- Remove this -->\n<Reference Include=\"Microsoft.VisualStudio.QualityTools.UnitTestFramework\" />\n\n<!-- Add this -->\n<PackageReference Include=\"MSTest\" Version=\"3.8.2\" />\n```\n\n### Test code\n\n**No changes needed.** MSTest v3 keeps the same namespace (`Microsoft.VisualStudio.TestTools.UnitTesting`) and the same attributes (`[TestClass]`, `[TestMethod]`, `[Timeout]`), so your `OrderServiceTests.cs` is already compatible.\n\nWant me to apply these changes?","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"b9245d4d-3702-4cfc-97fa-f1726e2504d0","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user wants to upgrade from the old MSTest (assembly reference to `Microsoft.VisualStudio.QualityTools.UnitTestFramework`) to MSTest v3.\n\nHere's what needs to change:\n\n1. **Remove the assembly reference** to `Microsoft.VisualStudio.QualityTools.UnitTestFramework`\n2. **Add MSTest v3 NuGet package** — MSTest v3 consolidated everything into a single `MSTest` package (replacing the old `MSTest.TestFramework` + `MSTest.TestAdapter` combo)\n3. **Update `Microsoft.NET.Test.Sdk`** to a newer version (or it may be pulled in transitively)\n\n\n4. **Check the target framework requirements** — I need to verify what the minimum supported framework is for MSTest v3, as it may have dropped support for older frameworks like net462.\n\nThe key steps are straightforward: remove the old assembly reference, swap in the unified MSTest NuGet package (v3.x), update the Test SDK, and keep the same namespace and attributes since MSTest v3 maintained backward compatibility there.","outputTokens":829},"id":"d4ebe641-7696-484f-ac57-ec2ce78af261","timestamp":"2026-04-03T01:06:39.464Z","parentId":"538df2bf-6d00-4670-889f-45cd3eab70c7"}
